        <etym xml:lang="ru">Вероятно, из %ifī-dīs%i ← %ipati-daisa-%i, буквально „указание“
                        (<mentioned xml:lang="x-oldirn"
                                ><lang/><w>dais-</w><gloss><q>указывать</q></gloss></mentioned>).<note
                        n="1"> PUT NOTE HERE </note> См. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ævdīsyn"/>
                ‘показывать’. Для семантики и образования ср. <mentioned xml:lang="de"
                                ><lang/><w>Ver-weis</w><gloss><q>попрек</q></gloss></mentioned> от
                        <mentioned xml:lang="de"
                        ><lang/><w>weisen</w><gloss><q>указывать</q></gloss></mentioned>.</etym>
        <etym xml:lang="en">Probably, from %ifī-dīs%i ← %ipati-daisa-%i, literally ‘indication’
                        (<mentioned xml:lang="x-oldirn"
                                ><lang/><w>dais-</w><gloss><q>indicate</q></gloss></mentioned>).<note
                        n="1"> PUT NOTE HERE </note> See <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ævdīsyn"/>
                ‘show’. As for the semantics and the derivation pattern, cf. <mentioned
                        xml:lang="de"
                        ><lang/><w>Ver-weis</w><gloss><q>reproach</q></gloss></mentioned> from
                        <mentioned xml:lang="de"
                        ><lang/><w>weisen</w><gloss><q>indicate</q></gloss></mentioned>.</etym>
